headline: This High-Yield Dividend Stock Could Deliver in a Downturn
summary: General Mills, Inc. (NYSE:GIS) is a global producer and distributor of well-known packaged food brands. Its wide-ranging product lineup includes cereals, yogurt, soups, meal kits, snack and nutrition bars, ice cream, frozen pizzas, pet food, and more.
